完畢的卡麥倫坡（尼可拉斯凱吉飾）為了保護剛懷孕的妻子免於小混混的騷擾，導致過失殺人被判了十年徒刑。<br />\n在獄中表現良好的他，終於在女兒八歲生日當天獲得假釋，卡麥倫坡希望能親自將生日禮物送到女兒手中，因此要求典獄官讓他登上空中監獄，以節省舟車往返的時間。 但這踏空中監獄正巧搭載一批全美最殘暴兇狠的犯人....<br />\n<br />\n1 15AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=r4H9ykDQE6JaJs7ebpxHnzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=b96c9b3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=r4H9ykDQE6JaJs7ebpxHnzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=0f55e181\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3a2c167f1a38f0c2c1c7594587bed8f6f3a568","tid":579558,"uid":144546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T17:10:41.000Z","msg":"空軍一號有一幕我覺得好震撼<br />\n到而家都會不時諗起<br />\n臨尾敵人射飛彈 個下個距離係必中<br />\n之後個戰鬥機機師諗都無諗就話：我去啦<br />\n之後用部機直接擋左粒飛彈<br />\n個飛彈太快 跳傘都跳唔切<br />\n咁就犧牲左<br />\n<br />\n其實依幕只係兩三個shot<br />\n但係係我全套戲最記得嘅一幕"},{"pid":"d9e51e2d5d5f1ae94234c57b7d730972f8a74ce5","tid":579558,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T17:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04496ba39203e0d14a3926d78cd2b72aa2c334a2","tid":579558,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T17:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"